{"tid":96410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【蝗軍殺到嚟 九龍新界冇得避】新春將至　6日5000支那旅行團湧港澳","createTime":"2017-01-26T23:26:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T09:41:19.000Z","uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"546cd62dd377234d044282526bc5e3d27ab9a5a8","tid":96410,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T23:26:47.000Z","msg":"農曆新年將至，大批<del>內地</del>支那旅行團赴港旅遊，據深圳皇崗出入境邊防檢查站稱，僅本月20日至25日，經皇崗口岸出境旅客逾33萬人次，當中赴港澳遊旅行團超過5000個。<br />\n<br />\n皇崗邊檢站預測，今年農曆新年期間(1月27日至2月3日)經皇崗、福田口岸出入境的旅客將逾152萬人次，其中皇崗口岸出境、入境高峰日分別為1月30日(年初三)和2月2日(年初六)；福田口岸入境、出境高峰日分別為1月29日(年初二)和1月30日(年初三)。<br />\n<br />\n皇崗邊檢站提醒出入境旅客合理安排行程，盡量錯峰、選擇口岸出行，避開上午8時半至11時半，下午5時至晚上9時等客流高峰時段出入境。另針對凌晨4至6時、上午8至9時、中午11至12時、下午3至4時等赴港乘飛機旅客高峰時段，當局加開通道，疏導旅客。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170126/bkn-20170126114603643-0126_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170126%2Fbkn-20170126114603643-0126_00822_001.html&d=%2By3f7Xfr8OKzgov72Jdd6EsIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=62ac6f0d\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170126/bkn-20170126114603643-0126_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"202bb83eb1e91ff0f1c3f16db07ddec0461f9b5e","tid":96410,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T23:28:29.000Z","msg":"屌你老母臭閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 行都冇撚得行<br />\n啲死生番 男女行路都柒下柒下唔帶眼<br />\n好撚似猛牛咁周圍衝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86dc579584f229fd5dee2c6565d00e1297fd37bd","tid":96410,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T23:33:33.000Z","msg":"姐係幾多人<br />\n5000團*30個左右<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f185e711049b5c2cdd177da8d200840476054171","tid":96410,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T23:36:47.000Z","msg":"受佔中影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5743263e0938fad38a2771b049c3bf027c7806cf","tid":96410,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T23:38:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4addb68e7a4c2b68a3537bc136b126caefa48351","tid":96410,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T23:45:09.000Z","msg":"窮果班就死都要返鄉下<br />\n中產果班為左避親戚<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8cc5da40e3ef72ae47d724d2ed1ad02f4cceb383","tid":96410,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T09:41:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}